{"tid":2152223,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"強人總統六度當選  20城市爆衝突一死  白俄鎮壓示威 濫捕3,000人","createTime":"2020-08-12T00:37:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-12T00:47:40.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2819e36f725ea8f38f36c5e5b38d707efdb00181","tid":2152223,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T00:37:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200811/U3PZBLHUKNOKVWQ7Y6ZOJBIXYY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200811%2FU3PZBLHUKNOKVWQ7Y6ZOJBIXYY%2F&d=xm989VH5JK0%2BokU91cWWf%2FcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=3aea0e73\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200811%2FU3PZBLHUKNOKVWQ7Y6ZOJBIXYY%2F&h=56b1b336\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200811/U3PZBLHUKNOKVWQ7Y6ZOJBIXYY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n強人總統六度當選  20城市爆衝突一死 <br />\n白俄鎮壓示威 濫捕3,000人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/9TvLTMvuOApzxadIRr5HvwEtFhs=/640x422/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MGCPVKN73ZMWG33UZ5EHJ3ABEI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F9TvLTMvuOApzxadIRr5HvwEtFhs%3D%2F640x422%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMGCPVKN73ZMWG33UZ5EHJ3ABEI.jpg&h=ebf22a0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n明斯克大批示威者築成人鏈，揮舞百年前國家未被蘇聯佔領時的國旗，勢要推翻今次選舉結果。路透社<br />\n<br />\n白俄羅斯總統選舉結束，一如外界預料，當局宣佈強人總統盧卡申科（Alexander Lukashenko）取得壓倒性勝利，奪得80.23%選票。首都明斯克與至少20個城市爆發反政府示威，警方重手鎮壓，據報造成至少一死數十傷，全國3,000人被捕。反對派表明不承認選舉結果，並聲言準備好長期示威對抗暴政。<br />\n<br />\n掌權26年的盧卡申科今次第六度當選，得票率拋離政壇新手季哈諾夫斯卡婭。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n80%高票當選 反對派拒接受<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：「歐洲最後獨裁者」蘇聯式管治<br />\n<br />\n她在記者會上表示：「我們不承認官方公佈的結果⋯⋯據我們得到的數據我們已獲勝。我相信自己雙眼，我看到大多數人。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n在前晚票站調查顯示盧卡申科大勝後，全國各地有成千上萬人上街抗議當局操。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n警方其後以暈眩彈、水炮甚至橡膠彈清場，亦向民眾揮棍狂毆。記者目擊防暴警拖走民眾。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/vBtTfkDy7VJ_iDeLj2sy-Lno0dM=/640x426/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YTOHBJ6PDYZSDUOW5VM65JOYVI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FvBtTfkDy7VJ_iDeLj2sy-Lno0dM%3D%2F640x426%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYTOHBJ6PDYZSDUOW5VM65JOYVI.jpg&h=d9708e4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有示威者受傷滿面浴血，由同伴揹離現場。美聯社<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警暴力清場 貨車衝向人群<br />\n<br />\n內政部其後公佈首都有50名平民及39位警員受傷，在全國拘捕約3,000人，其中約1,000人在首都被拘，指他們涉參加未經批准的。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n歐盟批評白俄羅斯「用超出比例兼不能接受的暴力對付和平示威者」。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n法新社/美聯社/路透社<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/VvCoMaQ_t87zqCvyIH2o6B3lo0c=/640x426/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3OUGVWOY34L24EQZVVFM3FQC3A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FVvCoMaQ_t87zqCvyIH2o6B3lo0c%3D%2F640x426%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3OUGVWOY34L24EQZVVFM3FQC3A.jpg&h=17ffd776&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n盧卡申科第六度當選總統。美聯社<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/yILwjtM1cZ-LMndK88ywUI39dYQ=/640x407/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/AVHMXNR7ZNYL2L6EB2L27ZGUW4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FyILwjtM1cZ-LMndK88ywUI39dYQ%3D%2F640x407%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FAVHMXNR7ZNYL2L6EB2L27ZGUW4.jpg&h=0f4db25b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n季哈諾夫斯卡婭（左）拒接受結果。路透社"},{"pid":"642f0e1cb286fd9dffb7c7152c0577c021602b80","tid":2152223,"uid":252142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T00:47:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}